alse`) for handling fancy styles. ![new](https://img.shields.io/badge/-new-brightgreen)\n\n---\n\n## 安装\n\n```bash\nnpm i -D vuepress-plugin-copy-code2\n```\n\n或\n\n```bash\nyarn add -D vuepress-plugin-copy-code2\n```\n\n## 从 V1 迁移\n\n名称从 `@mr-hope/vuepress-copy-code` 改为 `vuepress-plugin-copy-code2`. ⚠\n\n- [x] 选项 `delay`，控制页面加载和切换后注册复制按钮的延迟 ![新增](https://img.shields.io/badge/-新增-brightgreen)\n\n- [x] 选项 `locale` 用于国际化配置 ![新增](https://img.shields.io/badge/-新增-brightgreen)\n\n- [ ] 选项 `pure` (默认 `false`) 控制华丽的样式 ![新增](https://img.shields.io/badge/-新增-brightgreen)\n","readmeFilename":"README.md","_id":"vuepress-plugin-copy-code2@2.0.0-alpha.30","_nodeVersion":"16.13.1","_npmVersion":"lerna/4.0.0/node@v16.13.1+x64 (win32)","dist":{"integrity":"sha512-3thxJiiD8Tpz0l0Pc8voGYe8EW6UgRTKniNs9qBm3hzcSrQKYAXP6FzxW9gcKKqMK/G4UwgopFVWVAfJRXFlqg==","shasum":"037040accb23647df5ca565aa44c5c7fa9830e9b","tarball":"https://registry.npmjs.org/vuepress-plugin-copy-code2/-/vuepress-plugin-copy-code2-2.0.0-alpha.30.tgz","fileCount":20,"unpackedSize":25724,"npm-signature":"-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\r\nVersion: OpenPGP.js v4.10.10\r\nComment: https://openpgpjs.org\r\n\r\nwsFzBAEBCAAGBQJiEmOZACEJED1NWxICdlZqFiEECWMYAoorWMhJKdjhPU1b\r\nEgJ2VmpUhg/+K0Zl2j/UGy5V95H/0Y6nw0CQBuhTMolKCLTuh37LfVAuvY3b\r\nfa5Qr+rO4yYwu3G5Jr0m6StAZQq3nzqsL0sLUr7e3JMLHgYJbAQfpxTzpDct\r\n2fJoTPLLJYTbczKcprGR9rWAIRdjBM6oiD4xRi33F1kaDr0NgssukTE6S+fO\r\nxRE+44sRqpnBS8RvU6P+uBeqwI10AsoOuoOyEft5UPW0bHNZ99JHIbYjPLaF\r\nHxvt8jyRnZqAjmdahqOseuEhqrP341jUNslah5WPiYozOdqDu/SZ6McZsp9r\r\ndzzacIZLAyoQtwJvSFJHGnEJhAsbhtXqM3LHiEZtvY3Q4cSnGx78X8HNrYjh\r\nXKWKCqNjQpzzCSSovOWK7RQsgMTa+AGj6Dhnax3WZ7V7+o3NbU6RZScP4FUR\r\nchfqu+cGgOTyssYJp2TwGjRwchYCLJBBAw7yvZBkjRuPPAYNLgcJqBS7BOFB\r\np5uqvurYMnNG9Ol1GwoY0/Z+xYoIJ2DLpZcUoVW1ET2xsl5T4fYpHHE+nkL7\r\n5znWe5fwHg+7isd5PND6qJVLLG+I5s3WAQbYvQIwuiSJGUdoHYYF9wZuhNzD\r\nOENW/B2xMw7EotvqjWgWaBW31YaV6l9Hdl+yuY7nzpxeYrmwtjg9m9pNT0kD\r\n6bMJjn5YQO4Hal2NY/+mikSwZ898oraYxVY=\r\n=6aSS\r\n-----END PGP 